  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Now everyone's favorite TV Game Show is just for kids! It's got all the excitement of the adult version… Everything you see on TV and more, but the puzzles have been created just for the younger player.\n\nIt's your turn to be the contestant. Compete against your friends or match wits with the computer. Press the button, hear the theme music, spin the wheel, solve the puzzle and win a fortune, or hit bankrupt and lose it all. There are over 1000 puzzles to keep you guessing.",
